icient to induce\ndifferentiation in one scenario, an additional system perturbation (by\nstochastic fluctuations or directed impulses) of transcription factor levels is\nrequired in the other case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2006 12:45:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
